Package com.manaldush.telnet

Common part.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IClientSession
    Describe session object and its capabilities.
    ICommandParser
    Parser of telnet commands, realization of this interface describe style of telnet command and extract command text and options values from command string.
    ICommandParserFactory
    Factory for creation ICommandParser object.
    ICommandProcessor
    Processor of telnet command.
    ICommandProcessorFactory
    Factory, create ICommandProcessor object for command and session.
    IController<E extends java.lang.Cloneable>
    Describe interface of object, that control telnet module.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Command
    A specific execution for the command.
    CommandOption
    Option attribute of telnet command.
    CommandOptionValue
    Option value for command.
    CommandTemplate
    Template of telnet command, describe commands which system will process.
    Configuration
    Base configuration of service.

Package com.manaldush.telnet Description

Common part. In this package is described common interfaces and objects. Here is described common object model. Created by Maxim.Melnikov on 05.07.2017.
